reviewText: I have twin grand daughters age 3 and they adore sponge bob and quote him often. They now own several dvd's of spongebob.
good dvd set with many episodes that kids will love.  I buy the seasons for home use, and these cheaper dvd sets for on-the-go.

GREAT DVD!MY DAUGHTER CANT STOP WATCHING SPONGEBOB! GREAT FOR SPONGEBOB LOVERS!RECOMMENDED FOR ALL AGES!
ALWAYS ORDER SPONGEBOB FROM AMAZON.COM VERY SATISFIED CUSTOMER ALWAYS!
Both the kids and I loved the episodes on this. My only complaint is that it should have more episodes on it than what it does for the money.
Bought this for my daughter and she loves it, she watches it on long car rides and it keeps her entertained.
My 10 year old twins love this. One gave it to the other; they and their friends have watched happily multiple times.

Features 8 brand-new episodes! Episodes include:
1. To Love a Patty
2. Le Big Switch
3. Mermaid Man vs. SpongeBob
4. A Flea in her Dome
5. The Donut of Shame
6. The Blackened Sponge
7. Blackjack
